<h1>Dark Chocolate Macaron</h1>
<p>There is so much rich, decadent chocolate in this <strong>macaron</strong> that the chocolatey pleasure is just endless! </p><p>As you let the softness and the strength of our preciously selected cocoa waken your senses, you will feel a lot of pleasure and a little bit of guilt, for giving in to your dark (chocolate) side again!</p><p>There's no mistery why our Dark Chocolate Macaron is our longest-running pastry, in our whole collection, since our creation in 1992.</p>
